Got tickets at the last minute and decided to go 
as it is only an hour away.  Our seats got moved 
and got put on top row behind the stage.  Bad news 
was we stared at Elton's back but very close.  
There also was a huge screen right in front 
of us which was what I taped from instead of his 
back.  Not a single person walking in front of us, 
no problems at all. Great video and great concert
